# ingredients
Apple
Sugar
Cinnamon

# instructions
Peel, core, and slice apples. Add apples to large pot with about 2 cms of water just to cover bottom of pan and ensure apples don't burn. Add few dashes cinnamon, heat on low (3-5 level) until apples breakdown and can be broken up. Add more cinnamon and sugar to taste.